snippet.title: Yooka-Laylee - Multiplayer Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Revealing 8 mega multiplayer games set to feature in Yooka-Laylee, the next 3D platformer from key creative talent behind Banjo-Kazooie and Donkey Kong Country! Releasing April 11, 2017 on PS4, Xbox One and PC.
